Cleaner for browsing history, cache, cookie, and tracking. Configure cleaning on website level.

Cleaner is a handy and fast way to clean a browsing history

You can remove all data. Or remove a footprint of the last hour of browsing history.

Unlike many other tools, cleaner can remove data on website level.
